revision.text:
<!--호주_주,_준주_정보-->
{{TemplateMapping
| mapToClass = AdministrativeRegion
| mappings =
	{{ConstantMapping | ontologyProperty = country | value = Australia }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 이름 | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 원이름 | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 별명 | ontologyProperty = foaf:nick }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 표어  | ontologyProperty = motto }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 통치자 이름 | ontologyProperty = leaderName }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 전체 인구  | ontologyProperty = populationTotal }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 인구밀도 | ontologyProperty = populationDensity | unit = inhabitantsPerSquareKilometre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 전체 면적 | ontologyProperty = areaTotal | unit = squareKilometre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 토지 면적 | ontologyProperty = areaLand | unit = squareKilometre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 물 면적 | ontologyProperty = areaWater | unit = squareKilometre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 최고 높이  | ontologyProperty = maximumElevation | unit = metre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 최저 높이 | ontologyProperty = minimumElevation | unit = metre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 웹사이트 | ontologyProperty = foaf:homepage }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 주도 | ontologyProperty = capital }}
end}}
